---
import Layout from "/src/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  pageTitle="Marca Personal | Benjamin Espinoza"
  description="Mi marca personal, propuesta de valor y elevator pitch. Desarrollador Full Stack especializado en automatización de procesos e integración de IA."
>
  <section class="min-h-screen px-6 py-16 max-sm:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-sm:mb-16">
        <div class="relative mb-12">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-riptide-400 to-mint-300 rounded-3xl blur-2xl opacity-25"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-riptide-500/10 to-mint-500/10 border border-riptide-400/30 rounded-3xl p-12 max-sm:p-8">
            <h1 class="text-5xl max-sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-riptide-300 to-mint-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              🎯 Mi Propuesta de Valor
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl max-sm:text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
              Soy <span class="font-bold text-white">Benjamin Espinoza</span>, desarrollador Full Stack especializado en crear <span class="text-mint-300 font-semibold">soluciones inteligentes y escalables</span> que automatizan procesos y resuelven desafíos cibernéticos. Mi diferencial está en integrar <span class="text-riptide-300 font-semibold">Inteligencia Artificial</span> en cada proyecto para maximizar eficiencia y seguridad.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 30 segundos Elevator Pitch -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-sm:mb-16">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-mint-400 to-riptide-400 rounded-2xl blur-xl opacity-20"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-mint-600/20 to-riptide-600/20 border border-mint-400/40 rounded-2xl p-10 max-sm:p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 max-sm:gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="text-4xl">🎤</span>
              <h2 class="text-2xl max-sm:text-xl font-bold text-mint-300">Elevator Pitch (30 segundos)</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg max-sm:text-base text-zinc-200 leading-relaxed italic border-l-2 border-mint-400 pl-6">
              "Hola soy Benjamin Espinoza, estudiante de quinto año de Ingeniería Civil Informática. Me dedico actualmente a la <span class="font-semibold text-white">automatización de procesos</span> y resolviendo <span class="font-semibold text-white">problemas cibernéticos</span>. Lo que me diferencia es que no solo automatizo procesos, sino que integro <span class="font-semibold text-white">inteligencia artificial</span> para que esas soluciones sean más inteligentes y escalables."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Grid de 4 preguntas clave -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-sm:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl max-sm:text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-12 max-sm:mb-8 text-white">Mi Identidad Profesional</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-sm:gap-4">

          <!-- ¿Quién soy? -->
          <div class="group relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400/20 to-cyan-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-cyan-600/5 border border-blue-400/30 hover:border-blue-400/60 rounded-2xl p-8 max-sm:p-6 transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-4xl">👤</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl max-sm:text-lg font-bold text-blue-300">¿Quién Soy?</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold text-white">Estudiante de Ingeniería Civil Informática</span> en la Universidad Católica de Temuco, con <span class="font-semibold text-blue-300">4+ años de experiencia</span> en desarrollo web y soluciones tecnológicas. Apasionado por crear código limpio, arquitecturas escalables y sistemas que generan impacto real.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ¿Qué hago? -->
          <div class="group relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400/20 to-pink-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-600/5 border border-purple-400/30 hover:border-purple-400/60 rounded-2xl p-8 max-sm:p-6 transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-4xl">⚙️</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl max-sm:text-lg font-bold text-purple-300">¿Qué Hago?</h3>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-300">
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-purple-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Automatización:</span> Scripts e sistemas inteligentes</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-purple-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Ciberseguridad:</span> Identifico y mitigo vulnerabilidades</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-purple-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">IA/ML:</span> Soluciones con inteligencia artificial</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-purple-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Full Stack:</span> Apps completas frontend + backend</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ¿Qué problemas resuelvo? -->
          <div class="group relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400/20 to-emerald-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/10 to-emerald-600/5 border border-green-400/30 hover:border-green-400/60 rounded-2xl p-8 max-sm:p-6 transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-4xl">🎯</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl max-sm:text-lg font-bold text-green-300">¿Problemas que Resuelvo?</h3>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-300">
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span><span>Procesos manuales y repetitivos</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span><span>Desafíos cibernéticos y vulnerabilidades</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span><span>Necesidad de escalabilidad en sistemas</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span><span>Falta de inteligencia en automatización</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ¿Qué me diferencia? -->
          <div class="group relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400/20 to-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/10 to-orange-600/5 border border-amber-400/30 hover:border-amber-400/60 rounded-2xl p-8 max-sm:p-6 transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-4xl">✨</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl max-sm:text-lg font-bold text-amber-300">¿Qué Me Diferencia?</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-4">No solo <span class="font-semibold text-amber-300">automatizo procesos</span>, sino que <span class="font-semibold text-amber-300">integro IA</span> para que:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
                <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Aprendan</span> y mejoren continuamente</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Se adapten</span> a nuevos desafíos</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Escalen</span> eficientemente</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400">→</span><span><span class="font-semibold">Generen</span> decisiones inteligentes</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Competencias Clave -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-sm:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl max-sm:text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-12 max-sm:mb-8 text-white">🏆 Mis Competencias Clave</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-sm:gap-4">

          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-riptide-400/20 to-riptide-500/20 rounded-xl blur-lg group-hover:blur-xl transition"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-riptide-600/20 to-riptide-700/10 border border-riptide-400/40 rounded-xl p-6 max-sm:p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3 block">🤖</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-riptide-300 mb-2">Automatización de Procesos</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">RPA, Scripts, Orquestación inteligente</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400/20 to-red-500/20 rounded-xl blur-lg group-hover:blur-xl transition"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600/20 to-red-700/10 border border-red-400/40 rounded-xl p-6 max-sm:p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3 block">🛡️</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-red-300 mb-2">Ciberseguridad & Problemas</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">Vulnerabilidades, Hardening, Análisis</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400/20 to-purple-500/20 rounded-xl blur-lg group-hover:blur-xl transition"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600/20 to-purple-700/10 border border-purple-400/40 rounded-xl p-6 max-sm:p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3 block">🧠</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-300 mb-2">IA/ML & Inteligencia</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">LLMs, Prompt Engineering, ML</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400/20 to-blue-500/20 rounded-xl blur-lg group-hover:blur-xl transition"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/20 to-blue-700/10 border border-blue-400/40 rounded-xl p-6 max-sm:p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3 block">💻</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-300 mb-2">Desarrollo Full Stack</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">Frontend, Backend, DevOps</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400/20 to-green-500/20 rounded-xl blur-lg group-hover:blur-xl transition"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-green-600/20 to-green-700/10 border border-green-400/40 rounded-xl p-6 max-sm:p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3 block">📈</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-green-300 mb-2">Escalabilidad & Optimización</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">Arquitectura, Performance, DevOps</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-mint-400/20 to-mint-500/20 rounded-xl blur-lg group-hover:blur-xl transition"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-mint-600/20 to-mint-700/10 border border-mint-400/40 rounded-xl p-6 max-sm:p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3 block">🎓</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-mint-300 mb-2">Mentoría & Enseñanza</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">Compartir conocimiento, liderazgo</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Información de Contacto -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-riptide-400 to-mint-300 rounded-2xl blur-xl opacity-25"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-800 to-zinc-900 border border-mint-400/40 rounded-2xl p-12 max-sm:p-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl max-sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-white text-center">📍 Conecta Conmigo</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-sm:gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-riptide-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-riptide-400 text-xl">📧</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-1">Email</p>
                <a href="mailto:benjamintwo2002@gmail.com" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-riptide-300 transition">benjamintwo2002@gmail.com</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-mint-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-mint-400 text-xl">📱</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-1">Teléfono</p>
                <a href="tel:+56948553479" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-mint-300 transition">+56948553479</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 text-xl">📍</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-1">Ubicación</p>
                <p class="text-white font-semibold">La Araucanía, Temuco</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 text-xl">🎓</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-1">Formación</p>
                <p class="text-white font-semibold">Ingeniería Civil Informática - UCT</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/BenjaminEspinozaFK" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-4 py-2 bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-riptide-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center font-semibold transition text-sm">
              GitHub
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/benjamin-espinoza-52b3a6375/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-4 py-2 bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center font-semibold transition text-sm">
              LinkedIn
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/benjita_lou/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-4 py-2 bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-pink-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center font-semibold transition text-sm">
              Instagram
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@benjaminespinoza4879" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-4 py-2 bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-red-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center font-semibold transition text-sm">
              YouTube
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
